{"tid":1457750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由頭到尾就係冇做足準備，先一有乜風吹草動即刻散水，冇用腦分析情報冇gear以防萬一","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:48.000Z","uid":31539,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a06cc60d43c1c67a50a5d69a6424ddadfa8f538","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"先講mindset<br />\n再唔睇politics/history<br />\n都仲記得泰國黃衫軍掛?<br />\n人地直頭軍政府都唔撚敢清<br />\n因為心明玩機場就真焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n散水撚d流料就更加唔洗講<br />\n相信經過今次自己會計下數先<br />\n另外gear帶個豬咀都好啊大哥<br />\n放tg都唔洗急住走先<br />\n希望散咗水個d真心用下腦<br />\n成日掛咀邊d口號教條唔係放棄思考既藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e826eae69710ce135fc30d66043c9a71b0fbd767","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa5a35386f74070ad5b110529529e408b2cf5a8","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b2533e0cccb97cd1d291c17443d5e966179766","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f011c024b72d2a7b8a076c3ad24236cec156e613","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3041c571247c599cfc34e3fccab2519d9a76286d","tid":1457750,"uid":254361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:16:23.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用下個腦諗嘢<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n你哋唔好喺度發文喺度煽動<br />\n佢地成功分化我地了啦<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里而的大反派說了這麼幾句 <br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後這再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"20643675f8a634c7ea72db9f2de54678d84dde7d","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd1532d702a66a095f725f30906400bd22b6ca7","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c003b2e1b8f21982f3cf0c24b0df93fe6bcc63b9","tid":1457750,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}